Sat May 20 18:53:52 MDT 2017
1.  We need a way to show the user progress, at least in the simulations, 
because simuPOP can hang (or enter an endless loop), and the user has no
way of knowing that over time period t the simulation has not cycled at all.
Might be most simply a file with one line giving one integer, named after 
the temp_config file, and after each sim cycle, the current cycle number 
replaces the last in the file.  The sim gui checks the file during its
"sim in progress" state.

